title: Pork Schnitzel Banh Mi with Bacon, Potato Fries & Sriracha Mayo
description: Here’s a fresh new take on everyone’s favourite Vietnamese sandwich - the Banh Mi! Tender crumbed pork cooked to crunchy perfection is nestled inside toasted ciabatta with bacon bits, sriracha mayo, zingy pickled carrots and punchy coriander. Who wants a bite?
